  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>싸바리 박스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0fe7e964-43d2-475c-bd85-80ae4e62df64\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-de78aa7f-36f6-48b2-b3b6-d717e8425af1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-de78aa7f-36f6-48b2-b3b6-d717e8425af1\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDFfMjA3/MDAxNzU0MDQwNzQ5NDM2.KoIIsigJSG1QFzjkaJFYgmtoY5E1iGhhrA8Xr0u83Lwg.3-USqCN1VjMsDj7WcqUj0frWLfdcq1FIxMpUuvSI6-wg.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250801_131539961.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1058\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1411\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDFfMjA3/MDAxNzU0MDQwNzQ5NDM2.KoIIsigJSG1QFzjkaJFYgmtoY5E1iGhhrA8Xr0u83Lwg.3-USqCN1VjMsDj7WcqUj0frWLfdcq1FIxMpUuvSI6-wg.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250801_131539961.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">패키지 박스의 납품</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-47f4ad3c-da02-4ccf-a1eb-7189a9a228cd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f36ac70-5bd2-4957-a98d-ac8a8c175403\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단상자를 제외한 싸바리 박스 종류는 일단 부피가 큽니다. 완제품을 조립하여 납품하기 때문에 개당 부피가 있어 1,000개를 주문해도 몇 박스는 포장으로 소요됩니다. 통상적으로는 박스 포장을 하지만 이 박스 포장도 싸바리 박스의 부피와 크기가 모두 달라서 별도로 박스를 주문 제작하여 납품하는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e6e29b17-055c-4e6d-9ddd-d7d3d62ea2b3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-faee5a68-fc82-48d9-8682-c286ddcb2b95\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34f939dc-b900-4744-9f13-0474f0e31217\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b3f3381c-9e1c-4bd2-ab7a-85693b7f4555\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일반적으로는 팔레트 위에 싸바리 박스를 단으로 몇 단 쌓아서 양 모서리에 지대를 만들고 비닐로 여려 겹 포장하여 팔레트 별로 납품하는 경우가 대부분입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-e7cd129b-d2de-4607-851f-54f9f3630d21\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ba0df160-9e4a-493d-817e-7a8f9fbdb088\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDFfODYg/MDAxNzU0MDM5MjIxNDQ5.E9BOpsQVisREHDZx-kIIg-JjzzpttyGCRrpFt0BW88Ug.LEnGyOwtbI_Y1jiDEvDcFgLuX7t6BMRzijnaxVdOSNkg.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250801_131449221.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"4000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDFfODYg/MDAxNzU0MDM5MjIxNDQ5.E9BOpsQVisREHDZx-kIIg-JjzzpttyGCRrpFt0BW88Ug.LEnGyOwtbI_Y1jiDEvDcFgLuX7t6BMRzijnaxVdOSNkg.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250801_131449221.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-299cebe0-01ea-4f1a-9af5-09e620e6e512\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDFfMTEw/MDAxNzU0MDM5MjIyMDM5.YOPNnuoyJzwfkS768RuUiMhdG0rpNOtZCaYlP7RkUsIg.ZSVAAYiJLfPoN1IQvB1F_wdBa4zPSzmllJYc0MVtX5Mg.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250801_131449221_01.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"4000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDFfMTEw/MDAxNzU0MDM5MjIyMDM5.YOPNnuoyJzwfkS768RuUiMhdG0rpNOtZCaYlP7RkUsIg.ZSVAAYiJLfPoN1IQvB1F_wdBa4zPSzmllJYc0MVtX5Mg.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250801_131449221_01.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-12ed7229-07b1-4144-855f-842815defc76\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a34be46c-8877-4f0b-9a8d-5a093dcf74f9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-895cea57-64d9-4730-805f-662b7535cdb2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 방법을 사용하는 이유는 패키지는 통상의 경우 그냥 납품되는 경우가 없습니다. 그 패키지 상자 안에 제품을 담아야 하고 여러 가지 상황에 거 별도로 조립을 하는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bf29b6f4-d74c-47dd-b52e-2096a4d5d49f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-bf29b6f4-d74c-47dd-b52e-2096a4d5d49f\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDFfMjky/MDAxNzU0MDM5OTU3NjQ5.4GUoBD9pLMjcM6byVsQW08bf1JhJiLNVP3qBUWGO07cg.xha6EiC7o2y9dD1MdU0hPixCQOdsBmu39rcMMxSajXQg.JPEG/SE-bf29b6f4-d74c-47dd-b52e-2096a4d5d49f.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2250\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDFfMjky/MDAxNzU0MDM5OTU3NjQ5.4GUoBD9pLMjcM6byVsQW08bf1JhJiLNVP3qBUWGO07cg.xha6EiC7o2y9dD1MdU0hPixCQOdsBmu39rcMMxSajXQg.JPEG/SE-bf29b6f4-d74c-47dd-b52e-2096a4d5d49f.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a0c8b916-5bf6-44fe-9e45-e275f38ce83e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ab56685-6e29-4440-9101-78738cb66b4f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-67d6e898-767b-4a80-82fa-bb47a07a6a25\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 내용처럼 제품도 별도로 담고 이 안에 리플렛이나 소품들을 따로 넣을 수 있으니 제품을 뜯어서 넣고 다시 조립하는 과정을 거치게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f3b6d46e-b4a4-475d-bb45-040e843f373d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-92f4993f-3c30-4b95-9819-ca37dceef7dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c667a03-1768-4442-ad43-9b7f0d84fc07\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0eefb4e1-4475-47ea-b635-069d1f7a9ba1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 이유로 팔레트에 쌓아서 수량을 적어 납품합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e8a26f00-8d46-40f8-aaf3-5ed5b41a7fcf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-640fb2a0-05e0-4288-ba4c-a6c0a19e8f5e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e5ed048d-3b8a-4cc3-bdbf-3307c907edba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dc804ee6-54d9-4334-b555-5facb1950dfb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 요청에 따라 박스로 포장하여 납품되기도 합니다. 작업하고 다시 박스를 포장해 별도로 납품해야 할 때 이런 방법을 사용합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-3b2b0080-c724-4dff-976f-70819a44d33f\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-03fcb81b-1816-435e-b785-0b1a3416b937\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDFfMTUy/MDAxNzU0MDQwNzM3NTk4.c7xgD5erUOc61Wb9zrjR